ansport Service.</p><p>As reported by the Armyinform, the Chaplaincy Service of the Land Forces<a href=\"https://armyinform.com.ua/2024/02/22/kapelansku-sluzhbu-suhoputnyh-vijsk-ocholyla-zhinka/\">presented</a>A new manager.</p></div>", "source": "https://armyinform.com.ua/2024/03/29/shhe-29-vijskovyh-kapelaniv-zavershyly-navchannya-na-kursah-pidvyshhennya-kvalifikacziyi/", "title": "Another 29 military chaplains completed training in advanced training courses", "description": "The Ministry of Defense of Ukraine informs about it. As noted, within eight weeks ...", "author": ["Army Inform"], "categories": ["\u041d\u043e\u0432\u0438\u043d\u0438"], "tags": ["stoprussia", "\u0430\u0433\u0440\u0435\u0441\u0456\u044f \u0440\u0444", "\u0412\u0438\u043f\u0443\u0441\u043a \u043a\u0430\u043f\u0435\u043b\u0430\u043d\u0456\u0432", "\u0432\u0456\u0439\u043d\u0430", "\u0432\u0442\u043e\u0440\u0433\u043d\u0435\u043d\u043d\u044f \u0440\u0444"], "source_name": "ArmyInform"}